{"lastModified":1775541205922,"uri":"c::7646090758::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nDREAM is a stunning yacht that impresses with her elegance and comfort. Built by Cyrus Yachts, she has undergone a refit in 2023, ensuring she’s in pristine condition for her guests. Stretching 33.30 meters, this yacht offers smooth cruising at 16 knots, with a top speed of 24 knots. Moreover, equipped with stabilizers both underway and at anchor, DREAM provides a stable and relaxing journey.","blueprint":{"name":"DREAM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::16bbcc90-3608-11f0-9eff-27f8e3cdae5b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00eadbe0-8194-11f0-9f7a-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00e9f180-8194-11f0-9f7a-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00f27d00-8194-11f0-9f7a-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00fda090-8194-11f0-874f-7f5dc76acb40/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00e891f0-8194-11f0-9f7a-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00f58a40-8194-11f0-874f-7f5dc76acb40/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00f34050-8194-11f0-9f7a-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00f51510-8194-11f0-9f7b-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::00f42ab0-8194-11f0-874f-7f5dc76acb40/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c58489d0-79af-11ef-97cc-fdceee217c4c::assets::0100